---
title: Cajun Halloumi Wraps with Wedges and Sweet Chilli
description: Our Cajun Halloumi Wraps are a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cajun-halloumi-wraps-0948b6e2-ab5bcfa6.jpg
